version_description: Bug fixes and stability improvements, "Test" functionality improvements.

We are always looking to improve our products both by anticipating and by responding to our customers' needs. If you love using our app, please let us know with a review!

Fixed compatibility issues with iOS 9.

Bug fixes including: restore/previous purchase checked automatically at app launch, fixed short test sound beep while toggling On with audio playing, fixed Select Output behavior to block loop not allowing enable.
